Fantastic panaromic views
Oct 2023 • Couples
We visited this amazing viewpoint located in the Alfama neighborhood.

The panoramic views are amazing.

Many of the old buildings are survivors of the 1755 earthquake and one can see the modern building of the cruise ship terminal below.

Its just a short 5 minute walk from Baixa following the tram tracks.

We sat at one of the cafes located here and enjoyed a drink and a snack taking in the breathtaking views.

Brad
Hong Kong, China177,757 contributions
One of the beautiful viewpoints in Alfama
Apr 2023
There are a handful of very nice viewpoints in the Alfama district including Miradouro das Portas do Sol just off Largo Santa Luzia. You can reach this location by walking up Rua do Limoeiro, just past the Church de Santa Luzia and sister Miradouro there. From here you can view the lower Alfama neighbourhood, monument landmark buildings below and the Tangus River in the distance.

Views at Miradouro das Portas do Sol are remarkable and well worth spending some time to enjoy. While there you will see an interesting statue of Saint Vicente. There are some kiosks there for you to purchase and enjoy a drink or light bite to eat as well as artists selling their works. Plenty bars and eateries around as well if you fancy a proper sit down meal or rest while in the area.
Written June 10, 2023

Sofia R
4 contributions
Come for the view, not the food or service
Apr 2023 • Couples
Come here for the view and drinks if you are in the area but don’t go out of your way to visit.

Staff was pleasant but service really slow, we waited over 10 minutes to be seated and our drinks took 20min to get and the food almost an hour to be served.

Food was ok, nothing special. Price you pay is for the location and view, not the service or quality of food. The drinks were really nice and if I go back I’ll skip the food and just go for a drink and enjoy the beautiful view over Alfama.

I don’t discourage visiting, just be aware that it’s tourist-y with just ok food you could get anywhere else for half price and probably quicker, but anywhere else won’t get you this view.
Written April 12, 2023
